The '''Alopia Rift''' was a deep submarine trench on [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]]. Sufficiently deep to provide access to valuable mineral deposits and free of the dangerous creatures inhabiting many similar trenches, the submerged valley was the site of several [[Quarren/Legends|Quarren]] mining operations.<ref name="Strongholds" /> [[Bringe]] was in an accident in the Rift that removed his ability to breathe.

